etp is a master limited partnership that owns and operates one of the largest and most diversified portfolios of energy assets in the united states strategically positioned in all of the major us production basins etp owns and operates a geographically diverse portfolio of complementary natural gas midstream intrastate and interstate transportation and storage assets crude oil natural gas liquids ngl and refined product transportation and terminalling assets ngl fractionation and various acquisition and marketing assets  etp’s general partner is owned by energy transfer equity lp nyse etefor more information visit the energy transfer partners lp website at wwwenergytransfercom by accessing the links below you will find additional details about energy transfer partners our mission and values offers insight into what brings us together as an organization with a common sense of identity and makes energy transfer a great place to work business lines provides background on our key business segments including locations capacities and capabilities news releases provides access to recent news directors provides biographical information about our board of directors our asset map provides details about the reach and location of our pipeline systems and storage and terminal facilities market data copyright  quotemedia data delayed  to  minutes terms of use  energy transfer partners lp all rights reserved created by netreach® powered by cmscribe content management system cms contact us  energy transfer partners x you may need to reload the page to make it work correctly energy transfer partners                                                                                 reflects the closing of the merger between etp and sxl for more information click here homeinvestorscompany informationfinancial informationnews releasespresentationscorporate governanceinvestor email alertsinvestor contactsfaqk tax informationcustomersbusiness linescustomer toolscustomer contactspublic aware