ined that the probable cause of the accident included poor judgment on the part of the captain of the sun company helicopter and his failure to maintain safe separation from the senator’s airplane as of march  records maintained by the united states pipeline and hazardous materials safety administration phmsa show that sunoco has experienced  hazardous liquids incidents since  phmsa defines an incident as an event that involves a release of gas from a pipeline or of liquefied natural gas or gas from an lng facility that results in a death or injury necessitating hospitalization or property damage of  or more these  incidents resulted in  of property damage in terms of number of incidents sunoco has the worst safety record of  active pipeline operators who report operating data to phmsa in  sunoco along with other defendants was sued by the commonwealth of pennsylvania which alleged that sunoco and the other defendants polluted the waters of the commonwealth with mtbe a gasoline additive the commonwealth also alleged that the defendants including sunoco improperly accepted state funding to clean up spills which occurred prior to  and which were therefore not covered by the fund as a sponsoredit sunoco was penske racings sponsor of choice for many years particularly in the scca transam series where roger penskes sunoco camaros won the championship in  and  sunoco also sponsored penske porsches in the scca canam series and won the indianapolis  in  with penske and driver mark donohue in  nascar team owner billy hagan acquired sponsorship from sunoco for four seasons sterling marlin drove the  sunoco ultra oldsmobile during the  seasons and terry labonte for the  seasons in  sunoco became the official fuel of the nhra in  as part of the daytona update coinciding with the  daytona  a nascar version of the toyota camry with sunoco as its main sponsor appears in real racing  see alsoedit philadelphia portal companies portal  philadelphia refinery fire refinery at the time 